---
source: crates/mineral-tui/src/runtime/keymap.rs
description: "默认键位绑定表(和弦 → 动作,字典序;config 落地前的唯一真相源)"
expression: "lines.join(\"\\n\")"
---
+ → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(5))
- → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(-5))
/ → EnterSearch
= → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(5))
Backspace → BackOrClearSearch
Down → MoveSelection(Down(1))
Enter → ActivateSelection
Esc → BackOrClearSearch
G → MoveSelection(Last)
J → MoveSelection(Down(7))
K → MoveSelection(Up(7))
Left → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(-5))
Right → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(5))
Shift+Left → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(-30))
Shift+Right → SeekRelative(SeekDelta(30))
Tab → OpenQueue
Up → MoveSelection(Up(1))
_ → NudgeVolume(VolumeDelta(-5))
d → DownloadSelection
f → ToggleLoveSelection
g → MoveSelection(First)
h → BackOrClearSearch
j → MoveSelection(Down(1))
k → MoveSelection(Up(1))
l → ActivateSelection
m → CyclePlayMode
n → NextSong
p → PrevOrRestart
q → OpenQuitConfirm
space → TogglePlayPause
t → CycleLyricExtra
z → ToggleFullscreen
